OL,7,FPrices are stabilising and the IMF
OL,8,Fwants central banks and governments to
OL,9,Frespond accordingly. The former is by
OL,10,Fcutting interest rates. The latter, by
OL,11,F"urgently" sorting out their balance
OL,12,Fsheets.
OL,14,F"In many countries, primary balances,
OL,15,Fthe difference between fiscal revenues
OL,16,Fand pubic expenditure net of debt
OL,17,Fservice, needs to improve," Gourinchas
OL,18,Fsaid.
