OL,3,CUK urged to rein in spending as debt
OL,4,Cspirals beyond other developed
OL,5,Ceconomies
OL,7,FThe IMF names the UK, US, France,
OL,8,FItaly, South Africa and Brazil as
OL,9,Fcountries that need to take immediate
OL,10,Fsteps to prevent national debt from
OL,11,Fincreasing further.
OL,13,FThese nations borrowed heavily in
OL,14,Forder to support businesses and
OL,15,Fhouseholds during the pandemic and the
OL,16,Fenergy shock - they now find
OL,17,Fthemselves in a precarious position.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
