OL,3,CUK urged to rein in spending as debt
OL,4,Cspirals beyond other developed
OL,5,Ceconomies
OL,7,FGaurinchas said a lack of political
OL,8,Fwill, in parts of the world, to face
OL,9,Fthis challenge head-on, but insists
OL,10,Ffailure to act runs the risk of
OL,11,F"disorderly market imposed
OL,12,Fadjustments," similar to the sort Liz
OL,13,FTruss triggered.
OL,15,F"Success," Gourinchas added, requires
OL,16,F"implementing gradual and credible
OL,17,Fmultiyear adjustments without delay"
OL,18,Fwhile adding that aggressive tax rises
OL,19,For spending cuts would be "self-
OL,20,Fdefeating".
