OL,4,Cspirals beyond other developed
OL,5,Ceconomies
OL,7,FOf the advanced economies, only
OL,8,FJapan's debt-to-GDP ratio has risen by
OL,9,Fmore (63) than the UK's.
OL,11,FHas the UK government taken heed of
OL,12,Fthe IMF's warnings?
OL,14,FChancellor Rachel Reeves will travel
OL,15,Fto Washington later this week ahead of
OL,16,Fher Budget on October 30.
OL,18,FReeves is a recent convert to the
OL,19,FIMF's view of the UK's public finances.
