OL,7,FWhat is interesting is that throughout
OL,8,F2024, the IMF has repeatedly
OL,9,Fhighlighted the need for action in the
OL,10,FUK.
OL,12,FIn January, it explicitly called on
OL,13,Fthen-chancellor Jeremy Hunt not to cut
OL,14,Ftaxes further in his March budget. He
OL,15,Fignored the advice.
