OL,7,FThe forecast for economic growth in
OL,8,Fthe US next year is a little stronger.
OL,9,FThe forecast for the French and German
OL,10,Feconomies is a little weaker.
OL,12,FThe forecast for growth in the UK in
OL,13,F2025 is unchanged, although growth
OL,14,Fthis year is upgraded to 1.1% on
OL,15,Faccount of a stronger-than-expected
OL,16,Fprivate investment and public spending
OL,17,Fin the first half of the year.
OL,19,FSo, what could go wrong? As ever,
OL,20,Fquite a lot.
